<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Power of Attorney for Customs and Shipping</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
      line-height: 1.8;
      max-width: 850px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 50px 30px;
      color: #000;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      border: 4px double #000;
      padding: 25px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .header .subtitle {
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-style: italic;
    }
    .document-number {
      text-align: right;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .parties-section {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #fafafa;
      border-left: 5px solid #333;
    }
    .party-title {
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 16px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #333;
    }
    .party-details {
      margin-left: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .field-line {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .field-label {
      font-weight: bold;
      display: inline-block;
      width: 180px;
    }
    .preamble {
      text-align: justify;
      margin: 30px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 2;
    }
    .witnesseth {
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    .powers-section {
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .powers-section h3 {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #333;
      padding-bottom: 5px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .powers-list {
      list-style-type: none;
      counter-reset: powers-counter;
      padding-left: 0;
    }
    .powers-list li {
      counter-increment: powers-counter;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      text-align: justify;
      padding-left: 40px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .powers-list li:before {
      content: counter(powers-counter) ".";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      font-weight: bold;
      width: 30px;
    }
    .terms-section {
      margin: 30px 0;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
    }
    .terms-section h3 {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 0;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .closing-statement {
      text-align: justify;
      margin: 30px 0;
      line-height: 2;
    }
    .signature-section {
      margin-top: 60px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }
    .signature-block {
      text-align: center;
    }
    .signature-title {
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 60px;
    }
    .signature-line {
      border-top: 2px solid #000;
      padding-top: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .signature-name {
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 5px;
    }
    .witness-section {
      margin-top: 50px;
      padding-top: 30px;
      border-top: 3px double #000;
    }
    .witness-section h3 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .witnesses {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
    .witness-block {
      text-align: center;
    }
    .notary-section {
      margin-top: 50px;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 3px double #000;
      background-color: #fafafa;
    }
    .notary-section h3 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    .notary-field {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 50px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #666;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Power of Attorney</h1>
    <div class="subtitle">For Customs Clearance and Shipping Operations</div>
  </div>

  <div class="document-number">
    POA No: <%= poa_number %><br>
    Executed on: <%= execution_date %>
  </div>

  <div class="parties-section">
    <div class="party-title">Principal (Grantor)</div>
    <div class="party-details">
      <div class="field-line">
        <span class="field-label">Full Name/Company:</span>
        <%= principal_name %>
      </div>
      <div class="field-line">
        <span class="field-label">ID/Registration No:</span>
        <%= principal_id %>
      </div>
      <div class="field-line">
        <span class="field-label">Address:</span>
        <%= principal_address %>
      </div>
      <div class="field-line">
        <span class="field-label">Nationality/Country:</span>
        <%= principal_nationality %>
      </div>
      <div class="field-line">
        <span class="field-label">Contact Phone:</span>
        <%= principal_phone %>
      </div>
      <div class="field-line">
        <span class="field-label">Email:</span>
        <%= principal_email %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="party-title">Attorney-in-Fact (Agent)</div>
    <div class="party-details">
      <div class="field-line">
        <span class="field-label">Full Name/Company:</span>
        <%= agent_name %>
      </div>
      <div class="field-line">
        <span class="field-label">License/Registration No:</span>
        <%= agent_license %>
      </div>
      <div class="field-line">
        <span class="field-label">Address:</span>
        <%= agent_address %>
      </div>
      <div class="field-line">
        <span class="field-label">Contact Phone:</span>
        <%= agent_phone %>
      </div>
      <div class="field-line">
        <span class="field-label">Email:</span>
        <%= agent_email %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="preamble">
    <strong>KNOW ALL MEN BY THESE PRESENTS:</strong><br><br>
    That I/We, <strong><%= principal_name %></strong>, of legal age, and a resident of <%= principal_address %>, 
    hereinafter referred to as the <strong>"PRINCIPAL"</strong>, do hereby appoint, constitute, and designate 
    <strong><%= agent_name %></strong>, with offices at <%= agent_address %>, hereinafter referred to as the 
    <strong>"ATTORNEY-IN-FACT"</strong> or <strong>"AGENT"</strong>, to be my/our true and lawful attorney-in-fact, 
    for me/us and in my/our name, place, and stead.
  </div>

  <div class="witnesseth">
    — WITNESSETH —
  </div>

  <div class="powers-section">
    <h3>Powers and Authorities Granted</h3>
    <p>The Principal hereby grants to the Attorney-in-Fact full power and authority to perform the following acts:</p>
    <ul class="powers-list">
      <li>
        To prepare, sign, submit, and file all customs declarations, import/export documents, and related paperwork 
        required for the clearance of goods through customs authorities in <%= jurisdiction %>.
      </li>
      <li>
        To represent the Principal before customs authorities, port authorities, shipping companies, freight forwarders, 
        and any other relevant governmental or commercial entities involved in international trade and shipping.
      </li>
      <li>
        To make declarations, provide information, answer questions, and execute any documents required by customs 
        authorities for the importation, exportation, or transit of goods.
      </li>
      <li>
        To pay customs duties, taxes, fees, charges, and any other amounts due on behalf of the Principal, and to 
        receive refunds, drawbacks, or rebates of duties and taxes.
      </li>
      <li>
        To receive, store, transport, deliver, and take possession of goods, cargo, shipments, and related documents 
        on behalf of the Principal.
      </li>
      <li>
        To sign bills of lading, airway bills, delivery orders, warehouse receipts, and any other transportation or 
        storage documents.
      </li>
      <li>
        To engage customs brokers, freight forwarders, carriers, warehouse operators, and other service providers 
        necessary for the handling of the Principal's shipments.
      </li>
      <li>
        To challenge, appeal, or contest any customs assessments, rulings, penalties, or decisions, and to represent 
        the Principal in any administrative or legal proceedings related thereto.
      </li>
      <li>
        To request and obtain classification rulings, valuations, certifications of origin, and other determinations 
        from customs authorities.
      </li>
      <li>
        To execute post-entry corrections, amendments, or protests as may be necessary or advisable.
      </li>
      <li>
        To perform any and all acts, deeds, and things necessary or incidental to the effective exercise of the 
        powers herein granted, with the same force and effect as if the Principal had personally performed such acts.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="terms-section">
    <h3>Terms and Conditions</h3>
    <div class="field-line">
      <span class="field-label">Effective Date:</span>
      <%= effective_date %>
    </div>
    <div class="field-line">
      <span class="field-label">Expiration Date:</span>
      <%= expiration_date %>
    </div>
    <div class="field-line">
      <span class="field-label">Scope of Authority:</span>
      <%= scope_description %>
    </div>
    <div class="field-line">
      <span class="field-label">Territorial Jurisdiction:</span>
      <%= jurisdiction %>
    </div>
    <p class="legal-justify">
      This Power of Attorney shall remain in full force and effect until <%= expiration_date %>, unless earlier 
      revoked in writing by the Principal. Any revocation must be provided in writing to the Attorney-in-Fact and 
      to all relevant customs authorities.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="closing-statement">
    The Principal hereby ratifies and confirms all acts lawfully performed by the Attorney-in-Fact pursuant to this 
    Power of Attorney. The Principal agrees to indemnify and hold harmless the Attorney-in-Fact from any liability, 
    loss, damage, or expense arising from the exercise of the powers granted herein, except for acts of willful 
    misconduct or gross negligence.
    <br><br>
    This Power of Attorney is executed in accordance with the laws of <%= jurisdiction %> and shall be construed 
    and enforced in accordance with such laws.
  </div>

  <div class="signature-section">
    <div class="signature-block">
      <div class="signature-title">Principal (Grantor)</div>
      <div class="signature-line">
        Signature
      </div>
      <div class="signature-name"><%= principal_name %></div>
      <div>Date: <%= execution_date %></div>
    </div>
    <div class="signature-block">
      <div class="signature-title">Attorney-in-Fact (Agent)</div>
      <div class="signature-line">
        Signature (Acceptance)
      </div>
      <div class="signature-name"><%= agent_name %></div>
      <div>Date: <%= execution_date %></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="witness-section">
    <h3>Witnesses</h3>
    <p class="legal-center">
      Signed in the presence of the following witnesses:
    </p>
    <div class="witnesses">
      <div class="witness-block">
        <div class="mb-60">Witness 1</div>
        <div class="signature-line">Signature</div>
        <div class="mt-10">Name: _______________________</div>
        <div>Address: _______________________</div>
        <div>Date: <%= execution_date %></div>
      </div>
      <div class="witness-block">
        <div class="mb-60">Witness 2</div>
        <div class="signature-line">Signature</div>
        <div class="mt-10">Name: _______________________</div>
        <div>Address: _______________________</div>
        <div>Date: <%= execution_date %></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="notary-section">
    <h3>Notarial Acknowledgment</h3>
    <div class="notary-field">
      <strong>State/Province:</strong> _______________________________________
    </div>
    <div class="notary-field">
      <strong>County/Region:</strong> _______________________________________
    </div>
    <p class="legal-justify" style="margin: 20px 0;">
      On this _______ day of ______________, _______, before me personally appeared <%= principal_name %>, 
      known to me (or satisfactorily proven) to be the person whose name is subscribed to the within instrument, 
      and acknowledged that he/she/they executed the same for the purposes therein contained.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-40 legal-center">
      <strong>IN WITNESS WHEREOF,</strong> I have hereunto set my hand and affixed my official seal.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-60 legal-center">
      <div class="signature-line signature-line--center">
        Notary Public Signature and Seal
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10">Commission Expiration: _______________________</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>Document Generated: <%= Time.current.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %H:%M %Z") %></p>
    <p>This is a legal document. Please consult with legal counsel before execution.</p>
    <p>Keep multiple certified copies for customs and shipping authorities.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
